lead_paragraph: Olympiakos Piraeus began the new year in the same dominant way they ended the last by beating Panionios 3-1 away on Sunday to secure a club record-equalling 16th straight Super League victory.

headline.print_headline: Olympiakos Equal Club Record With 16th Straight Win
